 free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI_bufhbjrkwMVbr0rBh0-Nw66SIP2jtn0-KOQAcoBBEhWJXI=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbldhb1JpeUlBa3IwY3kySGh0cWtLNzhHMWVoQXxBQ3Jtc0tuLW9sbUw2QzY2X0l3dUdYOW1DZi1iMml2WE1yalU0ZGpUam5aME44bEhFVEh3cGJtRmktcVRnQ1dXRmpvUVVBc2dFbm9uVDV3MV82dXBpaTdKcXJVdkVLZTVTOGI3b2h1ZkpIM0QxbUFyWXdRakJPaw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=ASCPx0sjuwM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbldhb1JpeUlBa3IwY3kySGh0cWtLNzhHMWVoQXxBQ3Jtc0tuLW9sbUw2QzY2X0l3dUdYOW1DZi1iMml2WE1yalU0ZGpUam5aME44bEhFVEh3cGJtRmktcVRnQ1dXRmpvUVVBc2dFbm9uVDV3MV82dXBpaTdKcXJVdkVLZTVTOGI3b2h1ZkpIM0QxbUFyWXdRakJPaw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=ASCPx0sjuwM","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CI8CEM2rARgBIhMI_bufhbjrkwMVbr0rBh0-Nw66SIP2jtn0-KOQAcoBBEhWJXI=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbk0yNFRIRnRLcVpzeVpRVENJZW9obGdEbGlvd3xBQ3Jtc0tta3JhRS1pSy1Ga2hnRzlZR0E5Uzc0VmlSWW9OOHN6NDNNZE1hMlAtWGlyeGZYQXI3TDk2dnBwNE8wMmRDSlVLelU5eDJGbXNuQ1BqdWJ5QWY0ZEp2dVRkSGpsQmRCZVU2TmhMcE4wTlp4WUFOWEJxYw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26hosted_button_id%3D64QMBRBXQSV6G\u0026v=ASCPx0sjuwM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.co