ps://www.Lifeprint.com\nDonations appreciated (to help pay for hosting and related expenses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr...\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwj9u5-FuOuTAxVuvSsGHT43DrpIg_aO2fT4o5ABygEESFYlcg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbmdIRVIzaWZPdnVyY2c5ZHpvamxWTzVxcDRyZ3xBQ3Jtc0tuTnM4OGJ4WGdad2dxSDQ2ck1mSmdJajFIOXNqMW9vck82UkN1QXRRSnJKY2t0Zy1neWJtNEhZOWViQkJjdnFDS2hXdEdxc2h6YXZXaTRpczdpbloybFpWWDdzMnVFbUtzcGpjNHlhX0xZQjZDN3lLcw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=ASCPx0sjuwM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbmdIRVIzaWZPdnVyY2c5ZHpvamxWTzVxcDRyZ3xBQ3Jtc0tuTnM4OGJ4WGdad2dxSDQ2ck1mSmdJajFIOXNqMW9vck82UkN1QXRRSnJKY2t0Zy1neWJtNEhZOWViQkJjdnFDS2hXdEdxc2h6YXZXaTRpczdpbloybFpWWDdzMnVFbUtzcGpjNHlhX0xZQjZDN3lLcw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=ASCPx0sjuwM","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwj9u5-FuOuTAxVuvSsGHT43DrpIg_aO2fT4o5ABygEESFYlcg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_descripti